column.name: exceed_distance
column.Comment: 超过里程,不到起步距离，会是负数

column.name: address
column.Comment: remark requestor puts when placing order

column.name: order_vehicle_id
column.Comment: 订单车型(原service_type,类型为varchar),现在为枚举值

column.name: order_snapshot
pay_type
column.Comment: 前置支付支付方式（0:现金,1:微信支付,2:支付宝支付,4:纯钱包支付、5:个人钱包+微信、6:个人钱包+支付宝；）

column.name: pay_status
column.Comment: 支付状态：(0:待支付, 1:已支付，2:支付失败，3:退款中，4:已退款)

column.name: redpkt_status
column.Comment: 是否有红包，0:无，1:有,2:未发送，3:已发送(原redpkt,redpkt_send合并字段)

column.name: redpkt_code
column.Comment: 红包返回的code，根据这个code打开红包链接

column.name: tx_push
column.Comment: 最近推送时间，用于订单排序

column.name: unmatch_id
column.Comment: 0:'',1:客户已重下单,2:假单或测试单,3:客户选错地址、额外需求等,4:客户备注填写不清晰,5:客户不再需要用车,6:由于限行，司机无法完成,7:迟到、加价、态度差等司机问题,8:客户与司机搬运费或谈不拢,9:客户嫌平台价格贵,10:客户找了平台外的车,11:平台没开放客户需要的车型或者规格,12:客户手机关机或无人接听,13:未能在订单逾时前成功配对

column.name: perquisite_price_fen
column.Comment: 额外费用（后置支付中的额外费用）

column.name: rear_pay_status
column.Comment: 支付状态; 0:未支付，1:已支付,5:支付中

column.name: dashboard_status
column.Comment: 0 未跟进 1 已跟进 2 已认领

column.name: cash_received_time
column.Comment: 司机点击已收现金按钮的时间

column.name: driver_id_history
column.Comment: 历史司机id,如果只有a单为0,有b单为a单司机id

column.name: interest_history_snapshot
column.Comment: 历史司机的接单信息,只有a单为空串,有b单为a单司机接单信息json,包含除了driver_id_history的其它新增字段,格式{loaded_ts,loaded_latlon,pickup_latlon,pickup_ts,call_ts,reject_ts,arrive_start_ts,arrive_end_ts,reject_reason_text,reject_type,is_user_favorite,skip_rating,ab_create_time,order_fleet_status}

column.name: loaded_latlon
column.Comment: 司机装货经纬度，格式 纬度|经度,对应interest.loaded_latlong

column.name: pickup_latlon
column.Comment: 司机接单经纬度，格式 纬度|经度,对应interest.latitude，interest.longitude

column.name: call_ts
column.Comment: 司机打电话给用户时间戳,对应interest.txCalled_requestor

column.name: reject_ts
column.Comment: 司机或用户拒绝时间戳,对应interest.txReject

column.name: arrive_start_ts
column.Comment: 司机到达起点时间戳,对应interest.tx_arrive_start

column.name: arrive_end_ts
column.Comment: 司机到达终点时间戳,对应interest.tx_arrive_end

column.name: reject_reason_text
column.Comment: 司机或用户拒绝理由,对应interest.reject_reason_text

column.name: reject_type
column.Comment: 拒绝类型 1:司机拒绝，2:用户替换，3:用户取消，4:pannel取消,对应interest.reject_type

column.name: skip_rating
column.Comment: 是否跳过强制评分0:没1：是,对应interest.skip_rating

column.name: ab_create_time
column.Comment: a单或b单产生时间,当为a单时等于t_order.create_time,当为b单时等于vaninterest.txCreate

column.name: do
column.Comment: 合并表处理逻辑0:未查询,1:没有接单记录不需要处理 2:有接单记录,处理成功,3:有接单记录且超过2条,处理成功-1:有接单记录但找不到

column.name: do_version
column.Comment: 合并表处理逻辑版本号

column.name: invoice_status
column.Comment: 开发票状态 1: 未开发票 2：发票申请中 3： 已开发票

column.name: send_bill_time
column.Comment: 表示司机发送帐单时间

column.name: confirm_bill_time
column.Comment: 表示用户确认帐单时间

column.name: driver_add_fee_fen
column.Comment: 用户确认账单后金额（分）
